        dc:description           "Fig. 4. Orobdella tsushimensis Nakano, 2011 from Gageodo Island, KUZ Z213. A, Dorsal view of somites I–VIII; B, ventral view of somites I–VIII; C, dorsal view of somites XXV–XXVII and caudal sucker; D, ventral view of somites XXV–XXVII and caudal sucker; E, ventral view of somites XI–XIII; F, ventral view of gastropore and female gonopore; G, ventral view of gastroporal duct; H, dorsal view of male atrium showing position of ganglion XI. Scale bars: 1mm (A–E, G); 0.5mm (F). Abbreviations: ac, atrial cornu; af, annular furrow; an, anus; at, atrium; cl, clitellum; cp, crop; fg, female gonopore; gd, gastroporal duct; gp, gastropore; mg, male gonopore; np, nephridiopore; ph, pharynx." ;
